title: Use of wildcards
text: The use of wildcards (in this case the %) is especially useful in WHERE clauses to find any word with "Lake" within in regardless of letters that come prior.

title: Decimal Place
text: The decimal place that HouSiz is rounded to does not need to be specified, any number of decimal places can be rounded to.

title: Grouping and Filtering
text: To group results, it is more logical to first filter the relevant conditions and then group based on the filtered data.
